  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are looking at the effects of baby shampoo nasal irrigation on the movement
      of mucous in the nose in patients who have undergone sinus surgery for chronic sinus
      problems.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
